      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related KitchenAid and Whirlpool-family pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/whirlpool-refrigerator-repair/">Whirlpool refrigerator repair (parent brand) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/jennair-refrigerator-repair/">JennAir refrigerator repair (Whirlpool luxury) →</a></li>
